						<div class="postbody">It is probably undoing every write you do every frame. One way to get sound effects to play (this is a method someone once told me) is to find out where it buffers the values it writes to the apu and then overwriting that with your sound effects each frame. (giving your sound effect priority but otherwise the engine stil runs)</div>

